statements: SELECT * FROM nanostructures WHERE nanostructure_id = 1;
SELECT nanostructure_id, size FROM nanostructures WHERE shape = 'Sphere';
SELECT composition, size FROM nanostructures WHERE size > 10 ORDER BY composition ASC;
SELECT * FROM nanostructures WHERE shape = 'Rod' AND size BETWEEN 5 AND 15;
SELECT nanostructure_id, composition, shape FROM nanostructures WHERE composition LIKE '%oxide%' ORDER BY nanostructure_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM nanostructures WHERE size > 10 ORDER BY shape ASC
SELECT nanostructure_id, composition FROM nanostructures WHERE composition LIKE '%oxide%'
SELECT * FROM nanostructures WHERE size BETWEEN 5 AND 15 ORDER BY nanostructure_id ASC, shape DESC
SELECT MIN(size) AS smallest_size FROM nanostructures
SELECT * FROM nanostructures WHERE composition = 'carbon'
SELECT * FROM Nanostructures;
SELECT name, size, shape FROM Nanostructures WHERE composition IS NULL;
SELECT id, name, size, shape FROM Nanostructures ORDER BY size DESC;
SELECT * FROM Nanostructures WHERE shape = 'Sphere' OR shape = 'Cylinder';
SELECT name, size, composition FROM Nanostructures WHERE size > 100;
SELECT * FROM Nanostructures WHERE size > 10 ORDER BY name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, name, shape FROM Nanostructures WHERE composition IS NOT NULL ORDER BY size ASC;
SELECT name, size, shape FROM Nanostructures WHERE composition = 'carbon' OR composition = 'silicon';
SELECT id, name, size, shape, composition FROM Nanostructures WHERE id IN (1, 3, 5) AND composition IS NULL;

SELECT ns.name, ns.size, np.similarity_score FROM Nanostructures ns INNER JOIN NanostructuresComparison np ON ns.id = np.nanostructure1_id WHERE np.similarity_score > 0.8 ORDER BY np.similarity_score DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM nanostructure_size;
SELECT id, length, width, height FROM nanostructure_size WHERE id = 1;
SELECT aspect_ratio, surface_area FROM nanostructure_shape WHERE surface_area > 100;
SELECT material_name, density FROM nanostructure_composition WHERE density < 0.5;
SELECT id, shape_name, aspect_ratio, surface_area FROM nanostructure_shape ORDER BY aspect_ratio DESC;
SELECT * FROM nanostructure_size ORDER BY length DESC, width ASC, height
SELECT id, shape_name, aspect_ratio FROM nanostructure_shape WHERE aspect_ratio > 1.5 ORDER BY shape_name
SELECT material_name, chemical_formula FROM nanostructure_composition WHERE density > 2.5
SELECT id, shape_name, aspect_ratio, surface_area FROM nanostructure_shape INNER JOIN nanostructure_size ON nanostructure_shape.id = nanostructure_size.id
SELECT length, width, height FROM nanostructure_size WHERE length BETWEEN 5 AND 10 OR width BETWEEN 2 AND 5 ORDER BY length
SELECT * FROM nanostructures_sizes;
SELECT name, width, height FROM nanostructures_sizes ORDER BY width DESC;
SELECT * FROM nanostructures_shapes WHERE name LIKE 'N%';
SELECT id, name, material FROM nanostructures_composition ORDER BY id;
SELECT structure_id, size_id, shape_id, composition_id FROM nanostructures_info WHERE structure_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM nanostructures_sizes LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, name, width, height, depth FROM nanostructures_sizes WHERE width > 10;
SELECT name, shape_type, dimensionality FROM nanostructures_shapes WHERE dimensionality = 2;
SELECT name, material, density FROM nanostructures_composition WHERE density > 0.5;
SELECT ns.id, ns.name, ns.width, nc.material FROM nanostructures_sizes ns INNER JOIN nanostructures_composition nc ON ns.id = nc.id ORDER BY ns.width DESC;
SELECT * FROM Nanostructure_Size;
SELECT id, name, length, width FROM Nanostructure_Size WHERE width > 10;
SELECT id, nanostructure_id, shape FROM Nanostructure_Shape ORDER BY nanostructure_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM Nanostructure_Composition WHERE material = 'Gold';
SELECT id, description FROM Nanostructure_Information WHERE source LIKE '%research%';
SELECT * FROM Nanostructure_Size ORDER BY length DESC, width ASC, height DESC;
SELECT name, length, width FROM Nanostructure_Size WHERE length > 50 AND width < 30;

SELECT ns.name, nc.material, ni.description FROM Nanostructure_Size ns JOIN Nanostructure_Composition nc ON ns.id = nc.nanostructure_id JOIN Nanostructure_Information ni ON ns.id = ni.nanostructure_id WHERE nc.material = 'Gold';
SELECT * FROM Nanostructure_Information WHERE source LIKE '%research%' ORDER BY id ASC;

SELECT ns1.name AS nanostructure_1, ns2.name AS nanostructure_2, nc.comparison_result FROM Nanostructure_Comparison nc JOIN Nanostructure_Size ns1 ON nc.nanostructure_1_id = ns1.id JOIN Nanostructure_Size ns2 ON nc.nanostructure_2_id = ns2.id WHERE nc.comparison_result = 'Similar' ORDER BY ns1.name ASC;
